Kwanasaw am nawara sa o Fariseo a makey a omhawahaway sia do kahes da nia, “Ara o anohed no asa ka tawo a mapasiay so kakovot na do aran ango a rason?”
Tinbay ni Jesus a makavata sia, “Nalir nio paro pava do nakatolas a Chirin no Dios ta do nakapangamaog no Dios so tawo am namarin so mahakay kano mavakes,
