Vatan sia ni Jesus, “Ango itanyis moaya as kano sino o chitahen moaya.” Do vata ni Maria as hardinero awri daw o somisirin aw sia as vatan na sia dia o, “An ara imo o minpakaro sia dia am ivahey mo diaken an dino pinangayan mo sia ta ahapen ko.”
