Amna chinasi na yaken ni Jesu Cristo tapian maparin na ipavoya o karakoh no pasinsia na kano kaparin na a mapakabo as tomoroh so viay a abo so pandan do atavo a manganohed sia a aran do akma diaken a nah'ara dana so kapakagatos.
Dawa dadayen kano pamatohen o abo aya so pamandan a Patol! Iya o di aya voya as machimavoyvoh a kakawyoran a Dios. Amen.
